data.description:
Immaculately maintained home in a quiet country setting.   This cozy, one-level 1066 square foot home is move-in ready.  Situated on a large lot with a spacious yard and room for an RV, utility trailer or your outdoor toys.
Lots of special features in this home including  a new water heater in 2022, gas available to the kitchen for a gas range and to the deck for a gas bbq.  The home is also vented for two portable air conditioning units (two portable  AC units included in the sale).  Washer and dryer also included.
The setting is quiet and feels private, yet is only a short drive to the beach or to the valley.
